original_title: CZW: Ultraviolent Tournament of Death III: Banned... My Ass
overview: On July 24, 2004, the third CZW Tournament of Death (subtitled Banned...My Ass) was held in Smyrna, Delaware. This year there were no non-tournament matches held, however, the number of entrants rose from eight to twelve.
title: CZW: Ultraviolent Tournament of Death III: Banned... My Ass
